  <brief_title>To Evaluate the Therapeutic Equivalence and Safety of Azelaic Acid 15% Topical Gel</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Center, Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo Controlled, Parallel-Group Study, Comparing Azeliac Acid Gel and Active Treatments to a Placebo Control in the Treatment of Moderate Facial Rosacea.</official_title>
