  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A Multi-Center, Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo Controlled, Parallel-Group Study
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A Multi-Center, Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo Controlled, Parallel-Group Study, comparing
      AZELAIC ACID TOPICAL GEL 15% TO FINACEA® and both active treatments to a Placebo Control in
      the treatment of Moderate of Facial Rosacea.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
